  Gates of Olympus!
  -----------------

Copyright 2010, Rehno Lindeque, Theunis Kotze.

Gates of Olympus is a 3D multi-layer tower defense game.
As one of the wardens of Zeus's cloudy gates it is your sacred duty to protect earth from the heavenly beasts that roam the skies.



Please visit http://gatesofolympus.com to play the game or for further information.


